{"tid":1379713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上環住戶：警察民居放催淚彈「完全無腦，引起市民恐慌」","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T04:26:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":104,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c00645eef6280feaa5106e4f37cae393a9559a02","tid":1379713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190729/s00001/4dc2c91cd0237489cc5dc4981af5542d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F4dc2c91cd0237489cc5dc4981af5542d.jpg&h=169798aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190729/s00001/4dc18fe6ce7bf7df3e9511620bb61399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F4dc18fe6ce7bf7df3e9511620bb61399.jpg&h=51e58569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190729/s00001/4dc00aacd29c20d150c5b149a91eec9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F4dc00aacd29c20d150c5b149a91eec9a.jpg&h=bbc5f06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚（28日）在上環一帶，多番施放催淚彈驅散示威者，不少落在干諾道中和德輔道中之間的橫街窄巷，附近有民居。<br />\n<br />\n居於上環機利文街某大廈四樓的鍾太，批評警方在民居附近及橫街施放催淚彈，是「完全無腦，引起市民恐慌」，她說家中已關閉窗戶和沒開冷氣，但仍被催淚煙攻入家中，家裡的小朋友和老人家不停咳嗽和打乞嗤，警方不斷放催淚彈，家人沒走到街上，也要被迫吃下煙霧。<br />\n<br />\n本身居於西營盤正街的張先生表示，因港鐵昨晚封了西營盤站，他放工後要在上環站下車，甫離開A出口、即禧利街一帶，便受催淚煙波及，眼睛不停流淚。他批評警方在民居附近放催淚煙，「搞到民不聊生」，自己是出了地鐵站，才知道警方放催淚煙，警方也未有提供指示，讓他循沒有催淚煙的方向離去。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚11時許施放最後一枚催淚彈，但至今日（29日）凌晨2時，上環街頭催淚煙氣味仍揮之不去。"},{"pid":"f137bf13f1eca0bd97804bf2fbb2b19b22a436a6","tid":1379713,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564357190299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564357190299%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=a7018f3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190729%2Fs00001%2F1564357190299%2F&h=b1819f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190729/s00001/1564357190299/</a>"},{"pid":"77f8105fc4fe7f20cf29c89b897fe1afb5170385","tid":1379713,"uid":19557,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:58:32.000Z","msg":"真係仆街黎 民居係唔可以放呢d 野"},{"pid":"75299c6d347424b68378300c5d95f3ece08e20e8","tid":1379713,"uid":156632,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足</span></span> <br />\n大家緊記宗旨唔好被輕易帶動! <br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"17c40142c25a603690bda688eefe271de552d5b2","tid":1379713,"uid":156632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:06:46.000Z","msg":"班狗自立皇法架啦 又唔會有人追究佢地 佢地緊係自把自為<br />\n所以要制衡佢地必須獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef364baca185b7824e7ce86ba1aa4ae673cbdb3","tid":1379713,"uid":28279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:08:02.000Z","msg":"政府應該賠償損失傷害"},{"pid":"759ac46aa9c63ea0f714b3320527d74987d62be3","tid":1379713,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:15:32.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[八五三罷] 對8月5號罷工一事有感而發<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b8d71153ff46e1694c987526a4e933d3e9ee164","tid":1379713,"uid":52276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:35:10.000Z","msg":"啱囉，周街毒氣，返唔到工，唯有罷工！"},{"pid":"863f5886dd1c2dd1fe4e93fa0c6260e51be3cc11","tid":1379713,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"去索償啦"},{"pid":"7cb096188407b33d4ddd735ec09f8a71f21ff503","tid":1379713,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:43:24.000Z","msg":"再嘈開真槍"},{"pid":"db5a1123934eefb961d7b1fbc885f211e140f889","tid":1379713,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:47:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aac7bba8bcfe795a4791ce8fc3e8d1ccd2a4a143","tid":1379713,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30cb023dbc328bc01e2da5f183f2ce8d28530b55","tid":1379713,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"有錢人出聲 政府仲唔知驚？"},{"pid":"84a191b3868165598fa2c9b687047b7d3709aec3","tid":1379713,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"我支持告到政仆街"},{"pid":"467d0aa39bc29e287b8a363ba2822d097b1147c8","tid":1379713,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:19:33.000Z","msg":"We connect"},{"pid":"dfd7f87da7e512f4fcb4332e795bb83da4a3589d","tid":1379713,"uid":38757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"下午時都無咁狼, 入左夜, 基本上係催淚彈party ...."},{"pid":"82743f552c21f3f3fafbfc6bf06e8b383968086e","tid":1379713,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:26:52.000Z","msg":"以為唔出街就無事 <br />\n黑警見人就放蛋 理得你地死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" clas